Don't go!

280
00:34:44,372 --> 00:34:46,772
Who said that? Who did?

281
00:34:48,610 --> 00:34:51,204
Let me see who's a wanted convict.

282
00:34:54,249 --> 00:34:55,546
Don't you listen I said stop?

283
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:10,520
That man of taste is here again.

284
00:35:14,870 --> 00:35:15,971
Boss!

285
00:35:15,971 --> 00:35:17,305
Why are you here again?

286
00:35:17,305 --> 00:35:18,902
Boss, where's that painting
"The girl washing hair"?

287
00:35:22,377 --> 00:35:25,676
I'll get it for you at once.

288
00:35:28,917 --> 00:35:30,214
Boss, what are you doing?

289
00:35:31,019 --> 00:35:34,489
Why's it missing?
No one has ever asked for it.

290
00:35:34,489 --> 00:35:35,757
Well, come again tomorrow.

291
00:35:35,757 --> 00:35:37,659
I promise I'll find it for you.

292
00:35:37,659 --> 00:35:38,558
Well, I'll come again tomorrow.

293
00:35:51,339 --> 00:35:53,534
How could all 3 lanterns be blown out?

294
00:35:56,611 --> 00:35:58,602
When the wolf comes,
see how I'd cope with you.

295
00:35:59,815 --> 00:36:02,450
Can't you see the Yellow River's water,

296
00:36:02,450 --> 00:36:04,820
keeps flowing into the sea
without returning?

297
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:07,122
Can't you see the mourning of those,

298
00:36:07,122 --> 00:36:09,457
with grey hair before the mirror?

299
00:36:09,457 --> 00:36:12,358
Don't face the moonlight without a drink.

300
00:36:13,862 --> 00:36:15,297
Can't you see the Yellow River's water,

301
00:36:15,297 --> 00:36:16,598
keeps flowing into the sea
without returning?

302
00:36:16,598 --> 00:36:18,088
Can't you see the mourning of those,

303
00:36:18,667 --> 00:36:19,935
with grey hair before the mirror?

304
00:36:19,935 --> 00:36:22,804
Don't face the moonlight without a drink.

305
00:36:22,804 --> 00:36:24,704
Give and spend and God will send.

306
00:36:25,407 --> 00:36:26,241
1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7

307
00:36:26,241 --> 00:36:27,175
7, 6, 5, 4, 3, 2, 1

308
00:36:27,175 --> 00:36:28,076
1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7

309
00:36:28,076 --> 00:36:29,711
Understand the bible,
and you have the sword for ten years

310
00:36:29,711 --> 00:36:31,413
Then you've the credits.
I scare to leak out

311
00:36:31,413 --> 00:36:32,209
If you stay, then I'll go.

312
00:36:33,014 --> 00:36:34,106
I can hardly breath.

313
00:36:38,053 --> 00:36:39,145
Why is there no wolf?

314
00:36:42,958 --> 00:36:44,050
The wolf'ss coming!

315
00:37:45,987 --> 00:37:47,181
Nieh Hsiao Tsing...

316
00:37:53,361 --> 00:37:57,559
Hsiao Tsing...

317
00:38:07,642 --> 00:38:08,836
Open the door, Hsiao Tsing!

318
00:38:10,211 --> 00:38:11,313
Why are you here?

319
00:38:11,313 --> 00:38:12,447
I came because I heard the lute sounds.

320
00:38:12,447 --> 00:38:13,345
Come in quick!

321
00:38:15,951 --> 00:38:17,385
You can't come here.

322
00:38:17,385 --> 00:38:19,487
I'm leaving tomorrow,
I must say goodbye!

323
00:38:19,487 --> 00:38:20,388
Tomorrow?

324
00:38:20,388 --> 00:38:22,824
Yes, but I'll try to come to see you.

325
00:38:22,824 --> 00:38:23,722
Don't!

326
00:38:24,326 --> 00:38:25,593
Someone's coming!

327
00:38:25,593 --> 00:38:26,728
She has a sharp nose.

328
00:38:26,728 --> 00:38:28,525
Hide under the water,
and she can't smell you.

329
00:38:30,165 --> 00:38:31,154
In the water again?

330
00:38:45,146 --> 00:38:46,340
Sister Tsing!

331
00:38:47,415 --> 00:38:50,407
I know the matron's waiting impatiently.

332
00:38:51,186 --> 00:38:52,483
I'll go out after I've made up.

333
00:38:58,326 --> 00:38:59,418
Tramp!

334
00:39:03,064 --> 00:39:05,467
You're hiding a man!

335
00:39:05,467 --> 00:39:06,559
I am not!

336
00:39:06,901 --> 00:39:07,799
Don't deny it!

337
00:39:08,937 --> 00:39:10,029
Here's the proof!

338
00:39:11,740 --> 00:39:12,729
See for yourself.

339
00:39:14,309 --> 00:39:15,708
Why have you written such stuff?

340
00:39:17,312 --> 00:39:18,802
You obviously do that
in defiance of my order.

341
00:39:20,281 --> 00:39:21,475
I must punish you.

342
00:39:21,816 --> 00:39:22,805
You bitch!

343
00:39:23,952 --> 00:39:25,351
Don't forget the ordeal you suffered!

344
00:39:25,987 --> 00:39:28,387
Do as I tell you
or I'll destroy your ashes,

345
00:39:29,491 --> 00:39:30,583
and you'll evaporate like thin air.

346
00:39:37,298 --> 00:39:38,366
Tonight...

347
00:39:38,366 --> 00:39:40,163
get me a living being...

348
00:39:41,102 --> 00:39:42,592
to increase my vitality,

349
00:39:43,138 --> 00:39:44,230
and lengthen my span of life

350
00:39:45,707 --> 00:39:47,275
You'll be forgiven

351
00:39:47,275 --> 00:39:48,469
for this first offence.

352
00:39:49,577 --> 00:39:51,477
Bring medicine for your sister.

353
00:39:52,247 --> 00:39:53,236
Yes.

354
00:39:59,921 --> 00:40:03,124
You've been betrothed the Lord Black.

355
00:40:03,124 --> 00:40:04,819
In three days you'll be his wife!

356
00:40:05,427 --> 00:40:08,229
He's a bit old.

357
00:40:08,229 --> 00:40:10,398
But he's not good-natured.

358
00:40:10,398 --> 00:40:11,366
When he flares up,

359
00:40:11,366 --> 00:40:12,867
even we can't control him.

360
00:40:12,867 --> 00:40:13,902
After you marry him,

361
00:40:13,902 --> 00:40:14,891
you'll never return.

362
00:40:15,837 --> 00:40:16,805
Hsiao Tsing!

363
00:40:16,805 --> 00:40:17,772
Yes!

364
00:40:17,772 --> 00:40:18,864
Try it on.

365
00:40:19,808 --> 00:40:21,002
Your bridal dress.

366
00:40:25,914 --> 00:40:27,006
Come here and have a look.

367
00:40:50,105 --> 00:40:51,197
Seems there's some sort of smell.

368
00:40:52,006 --> 00:40:53,303
The smell of a living man.

369
00:40:57,645 --> 00:40:58,543
My dress is torn.

370
00:40:59,581 --> 00:41:00,673
Why are you so careless?

371
00:41:01,349 --> 00:41:03,084
I must wash my hand!

372
00:41:03,084 --> 00:41:04,176
Ching, let me help you.

373
00:41:04,786 --> 00:41:05,854
Thank you!

374
00:41:05,854 --> 00:41:06,843
Don't mention it.

375
00:41:08,089 --> 00:41:08,990
Why are you doing that?

376
00:41:08,990 --> 00:41:09,888
Sorry.

377
00:41:10,992 --> 00:41:12,494
Don't keep offending her.

378
00:41:12,494 --> 00:41:13,392
I didn't mean to.

379
00:41:14,062 --> 00:41:14,960
You haven't cleaned up yet.

380
00:41:16,598 --> 00:41:18,190
You did it on purpose, I give up.

381
00:41:18,766 --> 00:41:20,859
Take it off so I can mend it

382
00:42:01,576 --> 00:42:03,111
Tsing, what are you doing?

383
00:42:03,111 --> 00:42:06,512
I must take a bath before going out!

384
00:42:07,582 --> 00:42:11,279
If not I can't get you a living.

385
00:42:12,287 --> 00:42:13,686
Good girl.

386
00:42:14,222 --> 00:42:15,917
Ching, learn from her.

387
00:42:17,125 --> 00:42:21,118
I won't let you down tonight

388
00:42:24,599 --> 00:42:25,497
Come!

389
00:42:34,275 --> 00:42:35,264
Hurry up!

390
00:42:49,257 --> 00:42:52,658
3 days later after I get married,

391
00:42:53,328 --> 00:42:54,818
this room will be yours.

392
00:43:08,309 --> 00:43:10,300
Dress up! I won't look at you!

393
00:43:13,414 --> 00:43:14,649
Come!

394
00:43:14,649 --> 00:43:15,783
You...

395
00:43:15,783 --> 00:43:16,875
Go!

396
00:43:17,552 --> 00:43:19,020
I've a lot to tell you!

397
00:43:19,020 --> 00:43:20,214
Go to the temple first!

398
00:43:21,055 --> 00:43:22,257
I'll wait you there!

399
00:43:22,257 --> 00:43:23,246
Yes!
